monetization-ads/payments/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fplay.google.com%2Fabout%2Fmonetization-ads%2Fpayments%2F&d=wrEOEGOlledJIolh42HGtsVakpCEQgWe3bOYm8oES40%3D&h=a89d4b26\" target=\"_blank\">https://play.google.com/about/monetization-ads/payments/</a><br />\n<br />\nDevelopers offering products within another category of app downloaded on Google Play must use&nbsp;Google Play In-app Billing&nbsp;as the method of payment, except for the following cases:<br />\n<br />\nPayment is solely for physical products<br />\n<br />\nPayment is for digital content that may be consumed outside of the app itself (e.g. songs that can be played on other music players).<br />\n<br />\n不過VIP可以係網頁版用，冇得port鳩連狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f2fc07efb957bc9869b6441087b54834872c100e","tid":413340,"uid":23874,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-26T01:33:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/26/093319_37f9c758d11d5a3610bdb67484a47d9b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F26%2F093319_37f9c758d11d5a3610bdb67484a47d9b.jpg&h=b5f9736e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"be4f59534628b9e9a862d73a7008c331b0280427","tid":413340,"uid":42586,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-26T01:39:17.000Z","msg":"唉屌你老味 當日一大班高登仔過檔<br />\n就係想脫離牙糟高壓管治 五毛長期洗板 討論質素每況越下<br />\n過到嚟諗住有一番新氣象  當初連尼住講個啲承諾己經冇哂 <br />\n啲admin又失哂蹤<br />\n而家越搞越衰 成個連登都係MK 5毛 5P 細路 <br />\n乜鳩狗屎垃圾post都上到熱門過千正評<br />\n衰過高登<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n為咗錢 連狗真係乜都做得出"}]}